-- GCC Should Encourage Bank Mergers, Saudi Arabia Central Bank Governor Says
-- B y   A l a a   S h a h i n e
-- 2010-10-31T08:38:04Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-31/gcc-should-encourage-bank-mergers-saudi-arabia-central-bank-governor-says.html
Saudi central bank Governor Muhammad
al-Jasser said members of the Gulf Cooperation Council should
encourage mergers among banks in the region.  The remarks came in a speech read out at a conference in
Kuwait City today by Abdel-Rahman al-Khalaf, a central bank
official.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Alaa Shahine in Cairo at 
